{"tid":749212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國2025][大灣區][一帶一路]何志平在紐約申請撤銷部份控罪被駁回","createTime":"2018-07-20T00:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T00:56:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fef1d7dd20eab750cec01250d5387bf12fa8da54","tid":749212,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:35:49.000Z","msg":"何志平在紐約申請撤銷部份控罪被駁回<br />\n20.07.2018 08:18<br />\n<br />\n在美國被控賄賂非洲官員的民政事務局前局長何志平，申請撤銷部份控罪，被紐約地方法院駁回，意味已在美國被羈留八個月的何志平，需要就全部八項賄賂及洗黑錢罪名，在十一月受審。美國司法部指六十八歲的何志平，在2014年至去年一月，代表一間中資能源企業，涉嫌以約3百萬美元，分別賄賂乍得總統代比及烏干達外長庫泰薩，換取生意上的優待。何志平否認控罪。他多次申請保釋被拒。辯方律師指檢察官錯誤提出部份檢控，原因是何志平並非美國公民，但被法官駁回。"},{"pid":"10a3e992d275ba21df5a83111b1131384f15573d","tid":749212,"uid":30169,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:42:35.000Z","msg":"五毛下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a2ede1cf3d117e112aa9754751b75da6712969","tid":749212,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857429f369630e47ef218f62e9549301e5f55e6e","tid":749212,"uid":41500,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"撤乜銷呀佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為國捐軀無論中外都歌頌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係愛國既人,唔係隨時都準備好殉識咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049c5d1ef3291fede843096c2134926a2e4438d9","tid":749212,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00145c7c5486b074ec5948fee757873c2c80b979","tid":749212,"uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":